{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"661","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"Apple Watch豁免關稅 台鏈大補","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>2020-03-25 01:26 </span><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>經濟日報 記者吳凱中、蕭君暉<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>台北報導</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>&nbsp;<img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/APPLE%20WATCH.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 532px;' /></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>外電報導，美國貿易代表署批准蘋果提出的<span lang='EN-US'>Apple Watch</span>關稅豁免申請，從中國大陸出口的<span lang='EN-US'>Apple Watch</span>成品輸入美國，無須額外課徵<span lang='EN-US'>7.5%</span>關稅。 路透</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>外電報導，美國貿易代表署批准蘋果提出的<span lang='EN-US'>Apple Watch</span>關稅豁免申請，從中國大陸出口的<span lang='EN-US'>Apple Watch</span>成品輸入美國，無須額外課徵<span lang='EN-US'>7.5%</span>關稅。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>法人認為，美國市場為蘋果大本營，銷量具有舉足輕重的地位，<span lang='EN-US'>Apple Watch</span>免課額外稅率，意味蘋果能減少額外成本、擴大出貨，帶旺廣達、仁寶、美律、臻鼎<span lang='EN-US'>-KY</span>、台郡等供應鏈出貨。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>在此之前，由於美國對中國大陸發起貿易戰，<span lang='EN-US'>Apple Watch</span>等智慧手表被納入加稅清單，稅率提高至<span lang='EN-US'>15%</span>。今年<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>月，美國將<span lang='EN-US'>Apple Watch</span>等產品稅率從<span lang='EN-US'>15%</span>減半至<span lang='EN-US'>7.5%</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>法人看好，隨著<span lang='EN-US'>Apple Watch</span>獲得豁免關稅，蘋果在成本降低之下，先前要求供應商「共體時艱」，壓制供應商零組件、組裝價格可望放鬆，對相關供應鏈營運可望帶來正面的幫助。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>Apple Watch</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>原先由廣達獨家組裝，惟隨著銷量不斷增長，蘋果之後又找仁寶、立訊等組裝廠協助，除了因應龐大市場需求，蘋果引進中國大陸組裝廠，藉由新供應商加入，來取得更好的組裝價格。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>廣達考量<span lang='EN-US'>Apple Watch</span>利潤不佳，已經計畫性淡出相關組裝業務，釋出的訂單則由立訊及仁寶接手。由於市場普遍預估，今年<span lang='EN-US'>Apple Watch</span>出貨量仍能維持雙位數增長力道，對仁寶等供應商今年營收將有明顯幫助。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>蘋果執行長庫克之前表示，看好穿戴式應用的<span lang='EN-US'>AirPods</span>和<span lang='EN-US'>Apple Watch</span>等相關產品今年營收不錯，估計今年全年來自穿戴產品的營收將超過<span lang='EN-US'>400</span>億美元（逾新台幣<span lang='EN-US'>1.2</span>兆元）。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>法人分析，庫克先前就已經透露口風，預期<span lang='EN-US'>AirPods</span>和<span lang='EN-US'>Apple Watch</span>等穿戴裝置是蘋果成長力道最強勁的產品線，過往蘋果甚少針對單一產品釋出年度營收展望，此次釋出穿戴裝置年營收將超過<span lang='EN-US'>400</span>億美元的訊息，意味公司對相關產品線信心十足，為供應鏈業績注入強勁動能。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>儘管<span lang='EN-US'>Apple Watch</span>被豁免關稅，但蘋果部分產品仍在加稅清單內。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>蘋果目前已針對<span lang='EN-US'>HomePod</span>智慧音箱、<span lang='EN-US'>AirPods</span>無線藍牙耳機、<span lang='EN-US'>Mac</span>電腦等申請豁免關稅，並請求豁免<span lang='EN-US'>iPhone</span>零組件關稅項目。去年<span lang='EN-US'>12</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>iPhone</span>整機已得到關稅豁免。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/APPLE%20WATCH%20%E9%99%8D%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85.jpg' style='width: 400px; height: 426px;' />&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>經濟日報提供</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源：<span lang='EN-US'>https://money.udn.com/money/story/5612/4441004</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-03-26","clk_count":"230"}},"__N_SSG":true}